lev

Class LShrinkArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • lev.LImport
      • lev.LShrinkArray

  • public class LShrinkArray
extends LImport
    A special array with artificial min/max bounds. This allows smaller parts of the array to be passed around without actually copying the data to a new smaller array. It also provides extract functions which bump the lower limit of the ShrinkArray's scope, so that a following extract function can be called without having to worry about offset indexing.
